    <description>I think we should disable the [welcome page](https://user-media-prod-cdn.itsre-sumo.mozilla.net/uploads/gallery/images/2018-11-21-20-34-29-70625e.png) it fetches from Thunderbird&#39;s website to minimize attack surface. Sure it connects over TLS, but this isn&#39;t secure in certain threat models against advanced adversaries.

We can replace it with custom project art instead or just opt to retire it completely.

**`mailnews.start_page.enabled -&gt; false`**</description>
